qa_test_postfix
==========

Author:  Martin Mrazik <mmrazik@suse.cz>
Summary: (rd-)qa internal package for testing postfix

Test coverage:
- start/stop/restart daemon and check the result
- send e-mail to a local user and check that it was delivered
- send e-mail to a non-existent local user and check that it was bounced
- send e-mail with attachment
- send e-mail with attachment bigger than message_size_limit
- send e-mails so the mailbox_size_limit is exceeded
- check the newaliases command and sending e-mail to an alias



